
  Trinte Creator v<?- version ?> This is the help for generate controller.
  =======================================================================
 
  Usage: trinte -g controller <[namespace]modelName> [option(s)] [action(s)]

  Options:  

    [namespace]     Generate controller with namspace  
    [modelName]     The name (case sensitive) for the controller you want to create.
    force           force on exists controller
    [action]        Space separated actions list    
  
  Examples:
  
    # create controller Post without actions
    $ trinte -g controller Post
    
    # create controller Post with actions
    $ trinte -g controller Post index find create